{
  "2248280": {
    "name": "The Kaiyo Mission",
    "steam_appid": 2248280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/66bbac2ae4216dccc42edb93a279e525.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/66bbac2ae4216dccc42edb93a279e525.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/66bbac2ae4216dccc42edb93a279e525.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaiyō Mission 是一款关于在惊险的海洋世界水下环境中进行和平但危险的太空探索的游戏。玩家将经历三个不同的任务阶段，探索包括土星的卫星土卫二（Enceladus恩克拉多斯）在内的多个海洋世界的水下高原。他们将操控潜艇或潜水员，拍摄外星动物、植物和遗迹的照片。游戏提供了一个教程，完成前三个任务阶段后，还能解锁包含多个独立游戏的额外任务阶段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/75e57a2a7f1130377cf74bb7c1197ed7.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/75e57a2a7f1130377cf74bb7c1197ed7.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/75e57a2a7f1130377cf74bb7c1197ed7.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/2f2e2fe996db94840b5bde793584415a.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/2f2e2fe996db94840b5bde793584415a.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/2f2e2fe996db94840b5bde793584415a.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaiyō Mission 的主要特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个基于真实研究和硬核科幻冒险的独特故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏激发了玩家探索和平但充满危险的外星水下世界的好奇心，并完成各种研究任务。多种视觉模式、音效和音乐使游戏体验丰富且引人入胜。部分情节在一定程度上具有现实性，基于真实研究、科学以及硬核科幻设定。玩家置身于国际化的背景中，人类携手推动知识的边界……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/37d243412e374fea47e246e7dbdd06c7.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/37d243412e374fea47e246e7dbdd06c7.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/37d243412e374fea47e246e7dbdd06c7.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“在平稳下降后，居住舱被轻轻地放置在海床上，距离传送门不远，但又足够远，以避开可能成为妨碍的岩石。……探险者的新家有点像宇宙飞船。舒适和私人空间并不是优先考虑的事项。然而，所有设计都注重实用性，并优化支持在数百米深的海床上进行安全的潜水操作，可供多达十名潜水员在数天甚至数周内使用。”（摘自《Kaiyō Mssion ——Enceladus恩克拉多斯》）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在科幻游戏中使用非洲音乐</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很少有人将太空旅行和宇宙探索与非洲联系起来。这通常是因为许多人更倾向于将这些主题与古典音乐、西方音乐、甚至定制的“未来风”音乐联系在一起。《Kaiyō Mission》希望打破这种潜意识的偏见，使用振奋人心的音乐来增强游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用巴萨语本地化的独立游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Kaiyō Mission》可能是第一个以巴萨语（西非地区广泛使用的语言）为本地语言的独立游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于非洲传统游戏的外星星球小游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在额外任务阶段中加入了一些巴萨部落的传统游戏，以传承这些濒临失传的非洲文化部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/e72d3a36a0a2e34d13d9f8e98a6a3206.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/e72d3a36a0a2e34d13d9f8e98a6a3206.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/e72d3a36a0a2e34d13d9f8e98a6a3206.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索未知的水下世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/daebb1e6cf3f4acefab80221ed55b78e.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/daebb1e6cf3f4acefab80221ed55b78e.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/daebb1e6cf3f4acefab80221ed55b78e.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/662aaad03c2574ae6ef308bd43544579.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/662aaad03c2574ae6ef308bd43544579.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/662aaad03c2574ae6ef308bd43544579.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/4fa182bca23ba3f8c7a84c39a57cc9f2.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/4fa182bca23ba3f8c7a84c39a57cc9f2.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/4fa182bca23ba3f8c7a84c39a57cc9f2.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/bba26f03257c115474305a3d3434463d.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/bba26f03257c115474305a3d3434463d.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/bba26f03257c115474305a3d3434463d.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/01d1bfa3f0d677285ea82e1b2bd04a28.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/01d1bfa3f0d677285ea82e1b2bd04a28.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/01d1bfa3f0d677285ea82e1b2bd04a28.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拍照</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/5cd1ce01e8e3eed9e7a81af9a41970be.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/5cd1ce01e8e3eed9e7a81af9a41970be.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/5cd1ce01e8e3eed9e7a81af9a41970be.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/558a17fbb21d0a7519f2186cbe7768e1.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/558a17fbb21d0a7519f2186cbe7768e1.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/558a17fbb21d0a7519f2186cbe7768e1.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >意识到危险</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/819ed82ce8cd8ef20869e50cd4685bcc.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/819ed82ce8cd8ef20869e50cd4685bcc.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/819ed82ce8cd8ef20869e50cd4685bcc.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >传送门与旅程</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/a98b327a304057d060061bc0f6def334.poster.avif?t=1758553432\" width=786 height=442 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/a98b327a304057d060061bc0f6def334.webm?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/a98b327a304057d060061bc0f6def334.mp4?t=1758553432\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你是说，我们上个月登陆土卫二恩克拉多斯的两艘ESEL潜艇的其中一艘，在被部署后穿透冰层，发现了地下海洋中的生命，然后突然消失…最后，竟然上周在地球上被找到了？”JAXA深空探索负责人问道。（摘自《Kaiyō Mission——Enceladus恩克拉多斯》）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248280/extras/6649871faa139f1f622a8bfae1747078.avif?t=1758553432\" width=750 height=579 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
